reviews.review_text: WNEW FM It was great when the the Dead put out these great concerts on the best rock radio station in NYC history. I was at this concert the next day at school my friends were doing cat calls  from the concert.

- I pretty much bypass the 1st set, although Music Never Stopped is pretty awesome. Thanks for putting Scarlet Fire as one track, and the lack of Good Lovin doesn't detract at all, as it's not a spectacular rendition (you can hear it on other copies if you want to). Anyway, sweet 2nd set apart from that.
